      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Sifferus behdse Kah-\njahm us Jaëleß/ Eebera ta Kenti-\ntera Seewas Dsihwokli/ jo starp\nJabinn to Kehnizu no Azora/un\nstarp Eebera ta Kentexa Nam-\nmu bija Meere.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad isgahje Jaële Siffe-\nram pretti/ un fazzija: Nahz\neekscha Kungs/ nahz eekscha pee\nman/ ne bihstees/un wiꞥsch gahje\npee winnas eekscha Dsihwokli/\nun winna apsedse to ar kahdu\nApfeggu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥsch fazzija us to:\nDohd jelle man magkeniht Uh-\ndens/ jo man flahpst/ tad atdar-\nrtja winna weenu Peena.Span-\ngi/ un dsirdtja to/un apfedse to.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥsch fazzija us to:\nStahw Dsihwokta Durwis/ ja\nkahds nahk untew watzahs/ un\nfazzibs: Irr fkeit kas labban?\ntad fatki: newa ne weens.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad nehme Jaële Eebera\nSeewa weenu Nagli no ta Dsih-\nwokta/ un nehme weenu Westfe-\nru sawa Rohka/ un gahje pee ta\nlehaam/ un dsinne to Nagli zaur\nwinna Galwas.Mihfstumu/ ka\nwiꞥsch patt Semmê peekalts\ntappe/ bet wiꞥsch bija aisimdisis/\nun gurre/un nomirre.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un rangi Baraks dsih-\nnahs Sifferam pakkat/ tad is-\ngahje Jaële winnam pretti/ un\nfazzija us winnu: Nahz/ tad\nahdischn es tew to Wihrn/ ko tu\nkle/ tad nahze wiꞥsch pee tahs\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta pasemmoja Deew-\ntai Deena Jabinn/to Kananiteu\nKehnizu/ preefsch Israëta Beh-\nneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Israëta Behrnu Rol\nka stedsahs/un stiprinajahs pre-\nJabinu to Kananiteu Kehnizu\nteekamß tee Jabinn/ to Kananite-\nru Kehnizu isdeldeja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad dseedaja Debora u\nBaraks Abinoama Dehis te\nDeenâ/ un fazzija:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Eizeet to KUNGII tah\nAtreebschanas deht/ t\nwiꞥsch Israëlu irr atre-\nbis/ ka tee Landis paschi pee\nirr dahwajschees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Klaufajt juhs Kehnizu\nnenmeet wehra juhs Leeti-Ku-\ngi/ Es/ tam KUNGAM\ndseedaschu/ es dseedaschn tam\nKUNGAM tam Israëta De-\nwain Dseeemas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "KUNGS/ kad tu no Se-\nras isgahji/ un atnahzi no E-\ndoma Tihruma/ tad drebbeja\nSemme/ ir ta Debbes pileja/\ntahs Padebbettis pileja ar Uhden\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tre Kalni iskuße preeks-\nta KUNGA/ Sinai pats preek-\nta KUNGA ta Israëta Deew-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Samgara Anata Deh-\nDeenas/ Jaëleß Deewß/ bij Ze-\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
